254
00:11:11,603 --> 00:11:12,711
in WROCLAW?

255
00:11:12,970 --> 00:11:15,023
nisht in WR- DZIERZONIOW.

256
00:11:15,450 --> 00:11:16,422
DZIERZONIOW.

257
00:11:16,227 --> 00:11:17,740
nisht vayt fun WROCLAW?

258
00:11:17,239 --> 00:11:18,853
nisht vayt fun WROCLAW.

259
00:11:19,585 --> 00:11:22,312
un dortn hot men gevoynt a halb yor.

260
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:24,911
m'hot gemakht a bisele gelt

261
00:11:25,288 --> 00:11:27,442
m'iz arayngeforn keyn tsentral Poyln.

262
00:11:27,499 --> 00:11:28,556
keyn Lodzh.

263
00:11:31,077 --> 00:11:33,653
vos far a arbet hostu getun in

264
