vu?

265
00:11:35,464 --> 00:11:39,339
in Poyln, in di, di por, por khadoshim ven bist geven dort?

266
00:11:39,042 --> 00:11:42,039
ikh bin nisht geven keyn por khadoshim. geven elef yor in Poyln.

267
00:11:41,792 --> 00:11:45,178
ne- f- far, farn araynkumen tsurik in Lodzh.

268
00:11:44,239 --> 00:11:45,898
 m'hot gehandlt.

269
00:11:45,758 --> 00:11:46,511
yo.

270
00:11:45,898 --> 00:11:47,712
