s'ershte bin ikh arayngan arbetn in a shop

272
00:11:49,906 --> 00:11:51,169
fun shnayderay

273
00:11:51,613 --> 00:11:52,923
mikh avekgezetst

274
00:11:52,923 --> 00:11:54,243
neyen hoyzns

275
00:11:54,243 --> 00:11:55,523
bashtelte hoyzns

276
00:11:55,523 --> 00:11:56,673
un kostyumen.

277
00:11:57,891 --> 00:12:00,605
in dem iz arayngekumen a DEUTSCH

278
00:12:00,605 --> 00:12:01,935
iz arayngekumen

279
00:12:02,312 --> 00:12:03,943
mit a kupon skhoyre

280
00:12:04,118 --> 00:12:05,681
dort in dem shop arayn

281
00:12:06,852 --> 00:12:09,293
