282
00:12:10,243 --> 00:12:12,565
poylish gelt, zeks toyznt zlotes.

283
00:12:16,707 --> 00:12:19,384
⟨alzoy⟩, zey hobn nisht gevolt batsoln.

284
00:12:19,525 --> 00:12:21,949
