285
00:12:22,950 --> 00:12:25,002
bin ikh gegebn a gey aroys

286
00:12:25,549 --> 00:12:28,445
un ikh hob im gefregt, "gib mir" zog ikh "di adres

287
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:30,436
vu du gefinst dikh"

288
00:12:30,561 --> 00:12:33,103
hot er mir gegebn di adres vu er gefint zikh

289
00:12:33,261 --> 00:12:35,060
bin ikh geganen mit di froy

290
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:38,436
un ikh hob im shnel batsolt

291
00:12:38,728 --> 00:12:40,274
di zeks toyznt

292
00:12:41,665 --> 00:12:44,494
un ikh hob nisht gedronzhet ontsukukn dem kupon

293
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,041
hot men di froy farkoyft

294
00:12:47,368 --> 00:12:48,897
un genumen tsvelef

295
00:12:51,047 --> 00:12:53,420
un m'hot ongehoybn tsu handlen mit di DEUTSCHEN

296
00:12:53,848 --> 00:12:55,060
vayl far vos?

297
00:12:55,060 --> 00:12:56,790
zey hobn gehat rabirt

298
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,791
bay yidn

299
00:12:58,506 --> 00:12:59,597
gekoyft

300
00:12:59,603 --> 00:13:01,683
⟨azelkhene⟩ tishtekher, gekoyft

301
00:13:01,683 --> 00:13:02,988
sheyne

302
00:13:03,636 --> 00:13:06,448
⟨Lublin⟩ tishtekher. m'hot gekoyft

303
00:13:06,572 --> 00:13:08,186
UNK

304
00:13:09,222 --> 00:13:10,481
mashinen

305
00:13:10,774 --> 00:13:14,517
un s'zenen gekumen fun tsentral Poyln, fun Varshe, fun Lodzh

306
00:13:14,517 --> 00:13:15,848
fun KRAKOW

307
00:13:15,921 --> 00:13:18,626
zey hobn undz, zey hobn dos opgekoyft bay undz.

308
00:13:18,626 --> 00:13:19,993
iz men dort gevezn

309
00:13:19,993 --> 00:13:21,365
a halb yor

310
00:13:21,456 --> 00:13:24,912
azoy ikh hob shoyn gepakt dem DEUTSCH, hot men ongevizn

311
00:13:24,912 --> 00:13:27,305
dos ort dortn fun di DEUTSCHEN

312
00:13:27,413 --> 00:13:30,731
hob ikh shoyn opgelozt dem shop vos ikh hob gearbet

313
00:13:31,075 --> 00:13:32,031
un

314
00:13:32,543 --> 00:13:34,461
⟨m'vet aleynt⟩ vern balebatim.

315
00:13:34,483 --> 00:13:38,172
un di froy iz geganen, dort opgekoyft bay di DEUTSCHEN hot zi opgekoyft

316
00:13:38,179 --> 00:13:39,337
gantse pek.

317
00:13:41,571 --> 00:13:43,252
hot opgekoyft

318
00:13:43,444 --> 00:13:46,070
a T.V., zi hot opgekoyft radyos

319
00:13:46,178 --> 00:13:48,129
mashinen, tepekher

320
00:13:48,388 --> 00:13:51,026
zenen gekumen fun ts- fun tsentral Poyln

321
00:13:51,026 --> 00:13:53,259
un zey hobn bar undz dos alts opgekoyft.

322
00:13:53,535 --> 00:13:55,995
zenen mir dort geven a knap halb yor

323
00:13:55,995 --> 00:13:57,815
hot men gemakht a bisl gelt.

324
00:13:57,872 --> 00:13:59,621
m'iz arayngeforn keyn Lodzh.

325
00:14:00,758 --> 00:14:02,307
in Lodzh hot men getrofn

326
00:14:02,307 --> 00:14:03,451
mishpokhe

327
00:14:03,897 --> 00:14:05,747
vos zenen geven in di lagern

328
00:14:05,820 --> 00:14:08,412
hobn zey undz dertseylt di gantse historye

329
00:14:08,419 --> 00:14:09,915
vos hot pasirt

330
00:14:09,955 --> 00:14:11,501
mit mayn vayb's eltern

331
00:14:12,250 --> 00:14:13,858
damolt ⟨hot⟩ men gevoyr gevorn.

332
00:14:13,858 --> 00:14:16,819
bin arayngeforn keyn Pshedbuzh. di froy mayne iz geforn

333
00:14:16,819 --> 00:14:18,116
keyn Pshedbuzh.

334
00:14:18,139 --> 00:14:20,613
zi hot in Pshedbuzh keynem nisht getrofn.

335
00:14:22,628 --> 00:14:24,278
keyner fun di mishpokhe

336
00:14:24,278 --> 00:14:25,811
nisht geven keyn shum lebedike.

337
00:14:26,728 --> 00:14:27,987
dos iz gevezn

338
00:14:28,247 --> 00:14:29,855
onheyb

339
00:14:29,855 --> 00:14:31,172
dos iz gevezn

340
00:14:31,172 --> 00:14:33,084
in zibn un fertsikstn yor.

341
00:14:36,853 --> 00:14:38,686
un dos iz geven di ende.

342
00:14:38,828 --> 00:14:41,818
demolt hot men gevoynt in Lodzh bay elef

343
00:14:41,818 --> 00:14:43,748
beerekh elef yor.

344
00:14:44,667 --> 00:14:48,255
nokh dem hot men gezen me ken nisht farblaybn in Lodzh.

345
00:14:48,987 --> 00:14:50,449
es forn aroys

346
00:14:50,657 --> 00:14:52,186
kimat ale yidn

347
00:14:53,087 --> 00:14:56,000
trakht ikh mir "ale zenen naronim, vel ikh ⟨oykh firn⟩ a"

348
00:14:56,479 --> 00:14:58,059
zenen mir oykh geforn.

349
00:14:58,420 --> 00:14:59,679
ikh bin arayngekumen

350
00:15:00,090 --> 00:15:01,451
keyn TEL AVIV

351
00:15:02,318 --> 00:15:04,354
⟨zenen mir⟩ arayngekumen goldene mentshn.

352
00:15:05,929 --> 00:15:08,302
kh'hob gehat a bisl gelt, hob ikh gekoyft a shtub

353
00:15:08,916 --> 00:15:10,142
in RAMAT GAN.

354
00:15:11,076 --> 00:15:12,858
keyn arbet hot men nisht gehat.

355
00:15:13,641 --> 00:15:15,238
s'iz nisht geven ⟨tsurik⟩ keyn arbet.

356
00:15:15,430 --> 00:15:17,398
s'iz geven zeyer, zeyer troyerik.

357
00:15:18,737 --> 00:15:20,283
bin ikh ganen in BEER SHEVA.

358
00:15:21,488 --> 00:15:22,359
horkht.

359
00:15:23,563 --> 00:15:25,261
bin ganen in BEER SHEVA arayn.

360
00:15:25,487 --> 00:15:27,489
ikh hob farkoyft dos voynung.

361
00:15:27,698 --> 00:15:28,941
kh'hob mir gemakht

362
00:15:28,947 --> 00:15:32,130
ayngekoyft ⟨SOLELOT⟩. veyst vos heyst ⟨SOLELOT⟩ tsi nisht?

363
00:15:32,575 --> 00:15:34,779
vu me ma- vu me shtelt arayn hiner

364
00:15:35,308 --> 00:15:37,614
⟨hobn⟩ oyfgevaksn, hob gekoyft

365
00:15:37,975 --> 00:15:40,247
di EFROCHIM, kleyne hinerlekh

366
00:15:40,911 --> 00:15:44,499
un kh'hob dos oysgevaremt. kh'hob gemakht fun dem oyfes

367
00:15:45,315 --> 00:15:47,536
un m'hot dos farkoyft oyf fleysh.

368
00:15:49,737 --> 00:15:50,844
RAMAT GAN.

369
00:15:50,901 --> 00:15:52,464
veyst vu RAMAT GAN iz?

370
00:15:52,774 --> 00:15:55,198
NETN- NETANYA, nisht RAMA- NETANYA.

371
00:15:55,710 --> 00:15:58,471
zenen mir arayngeforn. m'hot dort farkoyft di oyfes.

372
00:15:58,478 --> 00:16:01,678
zey hobn farkoyft di oyfes, di TNUVA.

373
00:16:01,785 --> 00:16:04,664
di TNUVA hot farkoyft oyf undzer kheshbn.

374
00:16:04,806 --> 00:16:08,279
zey zenen geven di balebatim. undz ze'mir geven di arbetorer

375
00:16:08,279 --> 00:16:10,321
un zey zenen geven di balebatim.

376
00:16:10,321 --> 00:16:13,940
s'iz gekumen a zaytiker mentsh, hot er gegebn a fuftsik a funt

377
00:16:13,940 --> 00:16:16,690
hobn zey farkoyft mayns a kestl oyfes

378
00:16:16,690 --> 00:16:19,530
far dem prayz. zey hobn gemakht dem prayz.

379
00:16:19,530 --> 00:16:21,391
az azoy, vifl m'hot nisht gek-

380
00:16:21,391 --> 00:16:23,509
geleyzt, hot men alts tsugeleygt.

381
00:16:23,509 --> 00:16:25,281
azoy koym kh'hob gezen

382
00:16:25,281 --> 00:16:27,193
kh'ken shoyn mer nisht oyshaltn

383
00:16:27,587 --> 00:16:30,956
bin ikh arayngan arbetn in a kibuts, UNK PARDES.

384
00:16:31,975 --> 00:16:33,758
kh'hob gearbet in PARDES

385
00:16:36,582 --> 00:16:39,208
un di froy iz geforn keyn TEL AVIV.

386
00:16:39,754 --> 00:16:43,016
zi hot UNK, hot zikh ayngedungen dortn oyf a plats.

387
00:16:43,016 --> 00:16:45,553
zi hot ongehoybn tsu neyen kinder kleydelekh.

388
00:16:45,913 --> 00:16:48,252
un zi hot dos farkoyft oyfn SHUK HAKARMEL.

389
00:16:48,310 --> 00:16:49,215
UNK

390
00:16:49,913 --> 00:16:51,023
nokh dem

391
00:16:51,023 --> 00:16:53,568
vi di froy iz shoyn arayngeforn keyn TEL AVIV

392
00:16:54,402 --> 00:16:57,146
hob ikh likvidirt dem kibuts

393
00:16:57,658 --> 00:17:00,262
hob oyfgehert tsu arbetn in dem ki- kibuts

394
00:17:00,262 --> 00:17:04,014
un ikh bin arayngeforn keyn TEL AVIV. m'hot zikh ayngedungen bay a TEIMANER

395
00:17:04,746 --> 00:17:06,798
un ikh hob ongehoybn tsu arbetn

396
00:17:06,990 --> 00:17:08,536
eksport arbet.

397
00:17:09,943 --> 00:17:11,675
bay ⟨eynem, bay an importirer⟩

398
00:17:11,952 --> 00:17:13,279
un demolt

399
00:17:13,436 --> 00:17:15,877
hot men ersht ongehoybn oyftsuheybn dem kop.

400
00:17:19,073 --> 00:17:22,206
farn avekforn fun, fun Lodzh

401
00:17:22,109 --> 00:17:22,845
yo

402
00:17:23,493 --> 00:17:25,191
keyn IS- keyn ISRAEL.

403
00:17:23,663 --> 00:17:28,114
host, host, yo, vos, vos iz geven di, di, di la-

404
00:17:28,114 --> 00:17:30,333
tsushtand tsvishn di, di

405
00:17:30,333 --> 00:17:32,077
polyakn un di yidn dortn?

406
00:17:33,096 --> 00:17:37,342
veyst nisht vos di shtimung iz gevezn? ⟨dem⟩ shtimung iz gevezn a shlekhte.

407
00:17:37,382 --> 00:17:39,266
yidn hobn ongehoybn tsu forn.

408
00:17:40,369 --> 00:17:43,366
iz, hot zikh gemakht antisemitishkeyt

409
00:17:43,390 --> 00:17:45,274
az yidn zoln forn.

410
00:17:46,090 --> 00:17:46,804
zey hobn

411
00:17:46,804 --> 00:17:49,695
zey hobn tsugefirt azoy az yidn zoln avekforn

412
00:17:50,157 --> 00:17:53,340
zoln blaybn aleynt on a yidn. zey hobn undz nisht gedorfn.

413
00:17:54,561 --> 00:17:57,305
host bamerkt epes,

414
00:17:56,502 --> 00:17:58,279
zikher hot men bamerkt.

415
00:17:57,379 --> 00:17:58,166
yo

416
00:17:58,279 --> 00:18:00,008
vayl m'hot geflegt di ershte tsayt

417
00:18:00,008 --> 00:18:02,809
hob ikh geflegt shteyn oyf a, oyf a bazar

418
00:18:02,809 --> 00:18:03,889
oyf a mark

419
00:18:03,889 --> 00:18:05,439
hoyzn farkoyfn

420
00:18:05,547 --> 00:18:07,397
zenen tsugekumen antisemitn

421
00:18:07,825 --> 00:18:10,671
un zey hobn zikh gevorfn, geshpign oyf undz.

422
00:18:11,554 --> 00:18:13,066
kh'hob gezen me ken nisht.

423
00:18:13,090 --> 00:18:15,803
ikh hob likvidirt. shpeter hob ikh gearbet in di heym.

424
00:18:15,803 --> 00:18:17,336
kh'hob aroysgegebn arbet

425
00:18:17,443 --> 00:18:20,002
un ikh hob gearbet mit, mit sokhrim

426
00:18:20,548 --> 00:18:21,959
CUSTOMERS

427
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,318
azoy in Poyln, kh'hob zikh an eytse gegebn shpeter

428
00:18:25,662 --> 00:18:27,765
azoy lang ikh hob gezen az

429
00:18:27,872 --> 00:18:31,173
me ken vayter nisht arbetn dortn, vayl alts iz gevezn

430
00:18:31,247 --> 00:18:32,388
oyf treyf.

431
00:18:33,036 --> 00:18:34,577
m'hot nisht gekrign

432
00:18:34,577 --> 00:18:36,720
tsugeteylt keyn skhoyre

433
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,711
me zol kenen hobn an INVOICE

434
00:18:38,711 --> 00:18:40,804
me zol hobn vos oyftsuvayzn

435
00:18:40,804 --> 00:18:44,927
nor m'hot gemuzt koyfn umlegale skhoyre oyfn mark

436
00:18:45,844 --> 00:18:47,022
vos di

437
00:18:47,022 --> 00:18:49,433
froyen hobn genumen in di SHOPS

438
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:50,743
in di magazinen

439
00:18:50,743 --> 00:18:52,942
tsu dray meter, tsu zeks meter

440
00:18:52,999 --> 00:18:55,372
un dos hobn zey farkoyft oyf di bazarn

441
00:18:55,918 --> 00:18:57,616
⟨vu⟩ mayn froy iz geforn

442
00:18:58,011 --> 00:19:00,738
oyfn bazar. zi hot dos oyfgekoyft, arayngeleygt

443
00:19:00,846 --> 00:19:02,488
tsu eyne tsu a froy

444
00:19:02,488 --> 00:19:06,107
un farnakht hot zi dos aheymgefirt, un dos hob ikh geshnitn di skhoyre

445
00:19:06,107 --> 00:19:07,336
un ikh hob farkoyft

446
00:19:07,427 --> 00:19:09,564
un hot men gekent ekzistirn azoy.

447
00:19:09,790 --> 00:19:12,366
dos muz dokh zayn epes hent mit fis.

448
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,984
m'hot dokh ongegebn epes a barikht

449
00:19:14,984 --> 00:19:16,722
fun vanet me nemt di skhoyre

450
00:19:16,722 --> 00:19:18,002
vi azoy me tut

451
00:19:18,750 --> 00:19:22,085
un dos iz gevezn, dos lebn iz geven zeyer komplitsirt

452
00:19:22,429 --> 00:19:23,717
hot men gezen

453
00:19:23,717 --> 00:19:26,102
me ken nisht mer plats haltn.

454
00:19:26,142 --> 00:19:28,059
me muz dos alts likvidirn.

455
00:19:28,133 --> 00:19:29,713
me muz forn avek

456
00:19:29,787 --> 00:19:31,266
un demolt hot men

457
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:35,079
hot men zikh farshtanen az me darf avekforn fun Poyln.

458
00:19:35,592 --> 00:19:37,251
vos ikh hob gekent, hob ikh

459
00:19:37,251 --> 00:19:38,522
ibergefirt

460
00:19:40,131 --> 00:19:42,015
un m'iz arayngeforn

461
00:19:42,072 --> 00:19:43,500
keyn TEL AVIV

462
00:19:44,586 --> 00:19:47,837
un ikh hob dortn nisht gehat keyn arbet.

463
00:19:48,636 --> 00:19:50,177
kh'hob gemakht a feler

464
00:19:50,177 --> 00:19:52,241
vos m'iz arayn in KOLKHOZ.

465
00:19:52,382 --> 00:19:55,430
ober fun di ale felern hot men zikh alts aroysgekopyet

466
00:19:55,605 --> 00:19:57,607
vayl ikh bin nokh geven yung.

467
00:19:57,934 --> 00:20:00,310
bin shoyn alt geven tsvey un fertsik yor

468
00:20:00,310 --> 00:20:02,046
⟨hob⟩ ikh nokh geven yung.

469
00:20:02,558 --> 00:20:04,206
